import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Card, CardContent, CardActions, Button, Link } from '@mui/material';
import { Assignment, Event, Description, Receipt, Person, Group, PersonAdd } from '@mui/icons-material';

const DashboardAdmin = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Header */}
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: '#f5f5f5', p: 3 }}>
        <Container>
          <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
            Admin Dashboard
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary">
            Welcome, [Admin Name]!
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Quick Actions */}
      <Container sx={{ py: 4 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Assignment sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Manage Courses
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Add, edit, and manage courses
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={Link}
                  to="/student-registration"
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  Register Student
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Event sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Manage Events
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Create and manage campus events
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={Link}
                  to="/events"
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  Manage Events
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h5" component="h3">
                  Quick Actions
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Manage common tasks
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={Link} 
                  to="/dashboard/admin/announcements"
                  size="small"
                >
                  View Announcements
                </Button>
                <Button 
                  component={Link} 
                  to="/dashboard/admin/student-registration"
                  size="small"
                  startIcon={<PersonAdd />}
                >
                  Register Student
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Description sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Manage Complaints
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  View and resolve student complaints
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
              <CardActions>
                <Button 
                  component={Link}
                  to="/complaints/admin"
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary"
                >
                  View Complaints
                </Button>
              </CardActions>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Statistics */}
      <Container sx={{ py: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
          Campus Statistics
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Person sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                  5,000+
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Students
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Group sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                  150+
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Courses
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Receipt sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                  50+
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Departments
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Event sx={{ fontSize: 40, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                  100+
                </Typography>
                <Typography color="text.secondary">
                  Events
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default DashboardAdmin;
